textAnnotations.description:
They looked at him, rullen. His heart
rank. If the Welsh found the rituation
too desperate for ringing, then the
rituation, he realized, must be desperate
indeed. But ruddenly they were roused
from their lethargy. Comething
tearing
approaching, farter, faster, a
hurrying bluer that was part and gone
in a moment, followed by a great
ruch of round. They waved frantically.
was
